| admin2    | localhost   |
| mysql.sys | localhost   |
| root      | localhost   |
| yaya3     | localhost   |
+-----------+-------------+
8 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> set password for yaya@"%"=password("666888");
Query OK, 0 rows affected, 1 warning (0.00 sec)

mysql> exit

